of Earth is, in fact, curved, thereby making it one massive sphere, a globe, round ball.

00:04:43.030 --> 00:04:47.650
There were a few reasons they thought this, and they all come from

00:04:47.660 --> 00:04:52.060
observing the world around them, seeing things that you or I can see

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:56.360
anywhere in the world without any kind of complicated scientific equipment.

00:04:57.480 --> 00:05:01.620
