Or by looking at a lunar eclipse, where the Earth comes between

00:05:24.107 --> 00:05:28.047
the sun and the moon and forms a circular shadow against the moon.

00:05:28.747 --> 00:05:32.257
Or by climbing a tree or a high mountain and seeing

00:05:32.257 --> 00:05:34.967
that you can see further than you can on ground level.

00:05:35.907 --> 00:05:40.067
There are lots of different ways in which, even without any kind of modern

00:05:40.067 --> 00:05:44.457
technology, using simply your eyes and a rudimentary understanding of

00:05:44.457 --> 00:05:49.367
