So, was Rowbotham mad, a fraud, some kind of religious

00:09:14.658 --> 00:09:18.508
zealot, what was he trying to do by publishing this theory?

00:09:19.938 --> 00:09:25.008
Well, much like I described earlier, with the example of you or I being

00:09:25.018 --> 00:09:28.818
able to observe our surroundings and come to the conclusion that the

00:09:28.818 --> 00:09:34.218
Earth is round, Rowbotham did the same but came to a different conclusion.

00:09:35.667 --> 00:09:41.507
His was at least more scientific than our basic experiment of seeing a ship go over the horizon.

00:09:42.747 --> 00:09:47.767
Rowbotham found a long and straight canal outside Cambridge, in England.

00:09:48.657 --> 00:09:52.717
He got into the canal with his telescope, and watched

00:09:52.927 --> 00:09:55.867
as a boat went further and further away from him.

00:09:57.197 --> 00:10:03.637
If the Earth were round, Rowbotham pointed out, the boat would look like it was going down.

00:10:04.397 --> 00:10:09.097
But, shock horror, Rowbotham looked through his telescope and the

00:10:09.107 --> 00:10:13.557
