00:10:18.767 --> 00:10:22.627
Now, even though this can be explained through an understanding of

00:10:22.687 --> 00:10:28.387
physics, and how light refracts, Rowbotham was convinced that he was right.

00:10:29.237 --> 00:10:34.197
He got very excited about this idea, published this pamphlet, then

00:10:34.197 --> 00:10:38.777
the book, becoming the father of the modern “Flat Earth” movement.

