Now, as to the question of why, well this brings us into some interesting territory.

00:11:55.527 --> 00:12:00.237
Firstly, with recommendation-driven algorithms, they will tend to show

00:12:00.237 --> 00:12:03.677
you videos which you will continue to watch for long periods of time,

00:12:04.127 --> 00:12:08.887
