And in terms of societal reasons for this increasing belief, well, as you’ll know

00:14:16.547 --> 00:14:21.507
the world over, but certainly in the United States, there is increasing distrust

00:14:21.722 --> 00:14:27.167
of authorities, and an increasing idea that people should "do their own research”.

00:14:28.277 --> 00:14:34.177
The end result is that there is now a small but growing proportion of the population that is either

00:14:34.177 --> 00:14:42.847
sceptical about whether the Earth is a sphere or is 100% sure, utterly convinced, that it is flat.

00:14:44.007 --> 00:14:47.527
