Flat Earthers talk about going to Flat Earth conferences, socialising with other Flat Earthers, and

00:14:55.297 --> 00:15:01.547
losing friends and damaging relationships over their steadfast insistence that the world is flat.

00:15:02.767 --> 00:15:06.847
Now, this might be easy to ridicule if you don’t believe it.

00:15:07.897 --> 00:15:13.147
