00:15:13.147 --> 00:15:19.007
of hours researching it, and this thing wasn’t a trivial question of how to make the best

00:15:19.017 --> 00:15:25.217
chocolate cake or how to improve your English pronunciation, you had “discovered” that what

00:15:25.227 --> 00:15:31.837
practically every human believes to be true about the planet they live on…is a lie, well I can

00:15:31.837 --> 00:15:37.972
certainly understand why you might want to share that information with people, and how it would

00:15:37.982 --> 00:15:43.832
become something that could take over your life, permeating every aspect of your existence.

00:15:44.922 --> 00:15:50.452
And it would, I imagine, make life in normal society kind of tricky.

00:15:51.442 --> 00:15:56.082
