It is, in some ways, the most seductive of all of the

00:16:39.040 --> 00:16:42.570
conspiracy theories, simply because of its extremity.

00:16:43.660 --> 00:16:48.700
Other perhaps smaller scale conspiracy theories, involving things like the assassination

00:16:48.700 --> 00:16:56.440
of JFK or the moon landing or 9/11 or even, more recently, theories about where COVID came

00:16:56.440 --> 00:17:03.660
from, these are not quite so binary, there are different layers to them, where perhaps it’s

00:17:03.720 --> 00:17:08.970
