00:17:24.880 --> 00:17:31.330
It would be a conspiracy, a secret, that likely millions of people knew and were keeping secret

00:17:31.540 --> 00:17:37.840
right now: the pilots who were flying over the flat Earth, the astronomers who pretended to

00:17:37.840 --> 00:17:42.910
look at the solar system but knew full well that the truth was different, every employee of

00:17:42.910 --> 00:17:48.360
NASA, it would be the most monumental conspiracy involving the very nature of our planet.

00:17:49.700 --> 00:17:56.000
