00:17:56.030 --> 00:18:00.990
that you believe it, it’s harder to return to reality than almost any other conspiracy theory.

00:18:02.420 --> 00:18:08.170
Now, even within the Flat Earth theory, there are different theories about the makeup of the Earth.

00:18:09.140 --> 00:18:14.070
